      "date": "2018-10-09 20:27:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nInstead of just checking to see if it exists can we return some useful information like the current record number (cur_endrec from the relevant llog_changelog_user_rec)?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
