        "name": "Qian Yingjin",
        "email": "qian@ddn.com",
        "username": "qian"
      },
      "date": "2018-10-10 02:03:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nInstead of just checking to see if it exists can we return some useful information like the current record number (cur_endrec from the relevant llog_changelog_user_rec)?\n\nCurrent Write() into the changelog character device is used to handle special control operations. It does not contain any information. To return some useful information such as current record number, we need to implement the IoCtl() interface...",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
